<table border="0" width="100%"><tr align="left" valign="middle"><td><center><br /><center><font class="pn-title">Upgrades Abound</font></center><br /><br /></center><center>
Things have changed a little around the site. Most noteably, our old software was becoming unstable and unwieldly, so we chucked it to the weeds. Therafter a horde of gnomes descended on it and muttered something about it being &quot;a great find!&quot; I think it is safe to say that we can all agree that anything a gnome would be excited about is something that needed to be gotten rid of. Anyway, most of the changes weren't affect you gentle readers. Well, you might find our Roster a bit more up to date, but that's about it!. Enjoy!
</center>
<br><br>
Oh, and one more thing... if you were registered with the site before, you'll need to re-reigster. Sorry for the inconveinance.

