<a class="pn-title" href="modules.php?op=modload&amp;name=News&amp;file=article&amp;sid=8&amp;mode=thread&amp;order=0&amp;thold=0">My guild conquered the world and all I got was this lousy update...</a><br/></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>
<img src='themes//images/pixel.gif' height='5' width='1' border='0' alt=''/><br/>
</td></tr><tr><td class="article-table">We had a really great couple of weeks and hit some really big targets.<br />
<hr><b>Cursed Schmursed</b><br>Vyzh`dra the Cursed is an absolute monster of a mob.  We've been trying these past weeks to duplicate our kill again and finally managed to bring him down.  We almost lost at one point, but we stayed focused, regained control and finished him off.  We were rewarded with two absolutely insane BPs and another of the massive swords.<br />
<table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0><tr><td valign=bottom><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/News6/random/CursedCorpseLoot.jpg" width="263" height="135" alt="" border="0"><br></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=8596" target="new">Tase</a></b> and <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1840" target="new">Knosos</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Breastplate_of_the_Void.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=2457" target="new">Obfob</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Vyzhdras_Render_of_Souls.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr></table><br />
<hr><b>Every Little Thing Shei Does Is Magic...</b><br>We took down Shei for the second time in a really great fight.  I wish I'd remembered to take a shot during the fight.  It's a great room, carpet, marble, screaming 4-armed demigods.  You feel like you're brawling in the Taj Mahal.  Anyway, we got some really great drops.<br><table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0><tr><td valign=bottom><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/News6/random/SheiCorpseLoot.jpg" width="262" height="135" alt="" border="0"><br></td><td>Grats <b>Darkil</b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Ebony_Armguards.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr><tr><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=215821" target="new">Lbas</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Shadowsong_Cloak.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=16350" target="new">Juilin</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Shadowed_Torment.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr></table><br />
<hr><b>AoW, Ninjas and Justice</b><br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/News6/random/aowcorpse.jpg" width="710" height="300" alt="" border="0"><br><br />
The Avatar of War fell once again to our forces.  However we made one tiny mistake, accidentally released the corpse, and we got ninjaed.  The BoC, Mask, and Legs were taken.  Being LC, though, we did something about it.  We figured out who it was, and tracked him all across the globe and the moon.  Our members made damn sure the culprit didn't get away with it.  And he didn't.  All of the loot was returned to us and with any luck, the accounts involved will be banned.  If you're dying for details, some of them can be found on the public section on our boards.  This guy probably thrives on negative attention, and we have already given him too much.<br><br />
<table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0><tr><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=38513" target="new">Poplypop</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Flayed_Barbarian_Hide_Mask.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=170858" target="new">Tenbar</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Flayed_Barbarian_Skin_Leggings.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr><tr><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1832" target="new">Mwobley</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/War_Bow_of_Rallos_Zek.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=812" target="new">Krondath</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Blade_of_Carnage.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr></table><br />
<hr><b>Dainger Will Robinson!</b><br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/News6/random/Dain.jpg" width="200" height="289" alt="" border="0"><br><br />
Stumpy was up again, so we took him down.  We didn't get 20 adds this time, so it wasn't nearly as fun.  But it was still rewarding.  Dropped head and three cloaks (Salta ninjaed one before I took the shot).<br><br />
<table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0><tr><td valign=bottom><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/News6/random/DainCorpseLoot.jpg" width="255" height="136" alt="" border="0"><br></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td>Grats <b>Redlance</b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Belt_of_Dwarf_Slaying.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=135037" target="new">Chancy</a></b>, <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=61497" target="new">Gwedo</a></b> and <b>Gizan</b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Frostreavers_Embroidered_Cloak.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr></table><br />
<hr><b>Now we know why he's called Creator</b><br>He must be one hell of a smith with +30% to Blacksmithing skill.  I think he made the Ulak!  Now if we could only get the recipe...<br />
<img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/News6/random/creator2.jpg" width="336" height="269" alt="" border="0"><br><br />
<table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0><tr><td valign=bottom><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/News6/random/CreatorCorpseLoot.jpg" width="263" height="135" alt="" border="0"><br></td><td><br></td></tr><tr><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=21310" target="new">Skrabbit</a></b> and <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=140349" target="new">Grongl</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Hammer_of_the_Ironfrost.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=3461" target="new">Asky</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Glowing_Mithril_Ulak.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr></table><br />
<hr><b>Flashback Raid!</b><br>Absolutely nothing else was up that day, and something had to die.  We took our inspiration from LC raids of the past and squashed our old pals Telk and Gozz.<br><br />
<table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0><tr><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=16350" target="new">Juilin</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Unopenable_Box.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b>Xinae</b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Circlet_of_Silver_Skies.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr><tr><td>Grats <b>Suemdara</b> (friend of the Cult) !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Rekeklos_War_Sword.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=171516" target="new">Wango</a></b> and <b>McCorv</b> (friend of the Cult) !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Necklace_of_Nightstalking.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr></table><br />
