</td></tr><tr><td class="article-table">Things that died, in no particular order.<br><br />
<hr><br><br />
<b>Shei's Dead Jim</b><br><br />
We got our first kill of Shei Vinitras, a mob that requires a fair chunk of coordination and planning.  Alas, I missed it, so only get to show you the drops. If you want an image, just close your eyes and picture Morticia Addams with her hair in buns, four arms, a death touch, and much nastier children.<br><br />
<table cellpadding=5 cellspacing=0 border=0><tr><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=8596" target="new">Tase</a></b> and <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1548" target="new">Ebobulous</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Crys_Va_Mask.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td><td>Grats <b><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=183298" target="new">Wyen</a></b> !<br><img src="http://www.lotuscult.com/~quixotim/Loottemp/Ishinaear_Xiall.gif" width="330" height="135" alt="" border="0"></td></tr></table><br />
<hr><br><br />
<b>AoW #4</b><br><br />
We broke out of our slump with Clifford the Big Red Avatar.  It was a great fight, switches right on the money, solid dps.  We finally scored some caster loot off him too!  In the corpse shot you see 3/4ths of the Grobb Defensive Line.  Tried to take a screenshot of Dachunker, but the monitor started shuddering and sparking every time my finger got near the '-'; key.<br><br />
