</td></tr><tr><td class="article-table">Last night LC got the first kill of Vyzh`dra the Cursed on Quellious.  We had only attempted this version of him once, and then just to see what he was like.  We took some notes, made a few calculations, and came back to try him again.  Like a mongoose taking a cobra, we dodged and weaved and stabbed and poked.  When the dust settled we were standing - he was not.  We whooped and hollered at each other about how clever and bold we were, then we took his stuff.<br><br />
