</td></tr><tr><td class="article-table">Greetings dear readers, and welcome to the big huge giant update.  Proceeding in order of bigness mixed with recollection mixed with scribblings on the backs of eqatlas printouts:<br />
<hr><br />
<b>Usul, we have wormsign the likes of which even God has never seen.</b><br><br><br />
The Cult decided it was time to give the Burrower a shot.  I was not privy to the strategy but I heard something about a giant fishhook and a gargantuan trout.  I was unable to attend, but my correspondent Mengorn sent me this very nice snapshot.<br><br><br />
