<hr><br />
<br />
<b>Vengeance!</b><br><br><br />
We ventured into the Plane of Growth again to battle Tunare and her legions of prancing fuzzies.  This time it didn't take us three days to find her.  And she didn't despawn!  We also discovered her fatal weakness.  She's deaf.  Totally deaf.  We distracted her by making Dachunker run around naked on horseback and we all snuck up behind her, as you see in this shot.  It was over in about 5 seconds.<br><br><br />
