dunzeshugecack tells you, &quot;stroke me!&quot;<br />
sanityofdunze tells you, &quot;i'm lost, please come find me!&quot;<br />
lcwebsite tells you, &quot;omg update me, please?&quot;<br />
darkoor tells you, &quot;you're my idol. i look up to you more than to david hasselhoff even&quot;<br />
<br />
that's all, folks.  remember, keep your feet on the ground and keep reaching for the stars.  i'm audi 5000.<br />
